&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://news.hket.com/article/3954314/%E8%A9%A6%E9%A1%8C%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%EF%BD%9C%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%B3%BB%E6%9C%89%E8%A9%A6%E5%8D%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%E3%80%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%A0%88%E9%87%8D%E8%80%83%E3%80%80?mtc=20023"/><published>2025-05-25T17:45:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>https://ps.hket.com/article/3948248/%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E6%BD%AE%EF%BD%9C%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%9440%E5%B9%B4%E8%80%81%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E9%A4%A8%E3%80%8D5%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%80%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%98%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E7%B6%93%E5%94%94%E8%A6%BA%E5%B9%AB%E8%A5%AF%E5%92%97%E5%B9%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4?mtc=20023</id><title>結業潮｜元朗室內遊樂場5月中約滿結業　店主呻：被「熱心人士」日日投訴</title><updated>2025-05-25T18:11:00+08:00</updated><content type="html"/><link href="https://ps.hket.com/article/3948248/%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E6%BD%AE%EF%BD%9C%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%9440%E5%B9%B4%E8%80%81%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E9%A4%A8%E3%80%8D5%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%80%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%98%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E7%B6%93%E5%94%94%E8%A6%BA%E5%B9%AB%E8%A5%AF%E5%92%97%E5%B9%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4?mtc=20023"/><published>2025-05-25T18:11:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>https://news.hket.com/article/3954318/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%EF%BD%9C%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E6%96%99%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%85%A9%E9%99%A3%E9%A9%9F%E9%9B%A8%E3%80%80%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%A3%E6%BA%AB%E7%B4%8429%E5%BA%A6?mtc=20023</id><title>天氣預測｜天文台料有一兩陣驟雨　周日最高氣溫約29度</title><updated>2025-05-25T18:14:00+08:00</updated><content type="html">

&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-24T18:14:00+08:00 Updated on: 2025-05-24T20:33:19.027+08:00&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="article-detail-content-container"&gt;
&lt;div class="non-paywall"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;天文台預測周日（25日）大致多雲，有一兩陣驟雨，早上最低氣溫約24度，下午部分時間天色明朗，最高氣溫約29度，吹和緩北至東北風。隨後一兩日早上稍涼，部分時間天色明朗。下星期三及星期四驟雨較為頻密及有雷暴。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;span class="article-detail_inline-image block"&gt;
&lt;picture class="image-gallery-img"&gt;
&lt;source data-srcset="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_1024.jpg" media="(min-width: 1200px)"/&gt;
&lt;source data-srcset="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_600.jpg" media="(min-width: 992px)"/&gt;
&lt;source data-srcset="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_1024.jpg" media="(min-width: 630px)"/&gt;
&lt;source data-srcset="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_600.jpg" media="(min-width: 330px)"/&gt;
&lt;source data-srcset="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_300.jpg" media="(min-width: 0px)"/&gt;
&lt;img alt="" class="lazyload" data-alt="天文台表示，一道低壓槽會在下週中期為華南帶來大驟雨及狂風雷暴。（資料圖片）" data-link="" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_1024.jpg" src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3950000/3954318/royn20250412311_1024_1024.jpg" style="max-width:100%; height:auto;"/&gt;
&lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="article-detail_caption block"&gt;&lt;span&gt;▲&lt;/span&gt; 天文台表示，一道低壓槽會在下週中期為華南帶來大驟雨及狂風雷暴。（資料圖片）&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;而偏東氣流會在未來兩三日影響廣東沿岸，該區高溫天氣稍為緩解。一道低壓槽會在下週中期為華南帶來大驟雨及狂風雷暴。預料該低壓槽會在下週後期於南海北部一帶徘徊，該區仍有幾陣驟雨。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;span class="article-detail_inline-image block"&gt;
&lt;picture class="image-gallery-img"&gt;
